 to the village cemetery, the most recent complaint being from a young widow taking her children to visit their father’s grave and being confronted by trail bikes who so frightened the two little girls that they didn’t want to continue.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">This is only the latest in a long list of complaints.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">As a parish council we think our concerns are not being heard and our opinions brushed aside.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_GoBack"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Yours sincerely</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Dulcie Jones</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Clerk to the Council</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">25 September 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>